title: Home Foods
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Cambodian, Khmer, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Traditional Khmer homestyle food restaurant opened late-2014. Menu has the typical food selection seen around Asia, like fried rice, in addition to many local style dishes using local spices. Tell your server, "khnom num bous," which roughly translates to, "I eat vegetables," and kitchen can make something for you without fish sauce or meat, etc. Please send exact map coordinates to happycow!
